parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag control module can cause the airbag malfunction light to turn on, potentially leading to airbag deployment failure in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbag malfunction light on the instrument cluster
unclear if airbag will function in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause fires, airbag deployments, and other safety issues.
symptoms: Fires
airbag deployments
electrical system malfunctions
sensor lights blinking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Airbag sensor failures can cause airbag malfunction lights to turn on and potentially lead to airbag deployment failure in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbag malfunction light on the instrument cluster
airbag sensor failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Parasitic electrical draw can cause battery drain, leading to unexpected battery failure.
symptoms: Battery drain
electrical system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: CD changer malfunction can cause battery drain, leading to unexpected battery failure.

battery drain.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended engine speed increase can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Engine speed increase when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor can cause the airbag light to illuminate, indicating that the passenger airbag is not functioning properly, which can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger airbag light is on or flashing
the passenger airbag is not deploying
the airbag sensor is faulty
the passenger seat is not recognizing the presence of a passenger
the airbag warning light is illuminated on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking and melting of the dashboard can cause a glare on the windshield, which can lead to temporary blind spots and difficulty seeing while driving, potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The dashboard is cracking along the edges
the dashboard is melting and becoming sticky
the dashboard is shiny and creates a glare on the windshield
the dashboard is difficult to clean due to its sticky surface
the cracking and melting of the dashboard is widespread and affects multiple areas.
